{"tid":1945854,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陳梓維手下敗將葉傲冬再獲委任為人力資源規劃委員會委員","createTime":"2020-03-27T10:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T03:40:55.000Z","uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b7217f8c84a05fccce65abe2d7e575392b300b","tid":1945854,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:07:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/27/P2020032700270.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202003%2F27%2FP2020032700270.htm&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=d7160685\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/27/P2020032700270.htm</a><br />\n<blockquote> 特區政府今日（三月二十七日）再度委任十八名人力資源規劃委員會現任委員，並宣布委任三名新委員，任期由二○二○年四月一日至二○二二年十二月三十一日。<br />\n新委員 葉傲冬<br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民建聯 E19佐敦南 連任失敗&times;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n①. 陳梓維 1,516 50.99%<br />\n②. 葉傲冬 1,451 49.01%"},{"pid":"22ac2874b02fc4dff08642d35067a499050ade98","tid":1945854,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"牙冬幾把炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文匯報 助理總編輯<br />\n西九文化區管理局 董事<br />\n旅遊業監管局 委員<br />\n藝術發展諮詢委員會 委員<br />\n康樂及文化事務署場地伙伴計劃委員會 成員<br />\n油尖旺防火委員會 委員<br />\n人力資源規劃委員會 委員"},{"pid":"845a636799eff59367b955943acf8e4298f0525c","tid":1945854,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/85231274_170112921076666_6635551058720456704_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=aXR2BVMDBloAX8Peoyy&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=870a66ca49712d2d0e4dce4d2d9bdbaa&amp;oe=5EA399D1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F85231274_170112921076666_6635551058720456704_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DaXR2BVMDBloAX8Peoyy%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D870a66ca49712d2d0e4dce4d2d9bdbaa%26oe%3D5EA399D1&h=3060d3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過海路線方面，陳梓維不滿970（數碼港至蘇屋邨）及970X（香港仔至蘇屋邨）的班次問題，他表示自己是其中一名受害者，指表列時間最長為18至20分鐘，但最後卻等候了1小時。他又認為970及970X的一段彌敦道走線有重疊，建議970X可轉行其他道路，令其「快啲入西隧」。新城助理策劃經理冼志賢回應則明確表明不會考慮，因兩條路線「過咗華富就分道揚鑣」，「唔可以叫兩飛」， 若然接納建議會對另一邊乘客不公平。"},{"pid":"9b7551d997347f7b103a6d6bbbe66dd6ecbacc09","tid":1945854,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22ac2874b02fc4dff08642d35067a499050ade98","tid":1945854,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"牙冬幾把炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文匯報 助理總編輯<br />\n西九文化區管理局 董事<br />\n旅遊業監管局 委員<br />\n藝術發展諮詢委員會 委員<br />\n康樂及文化事務署場地伙伴計劃委員會 成員<br />\n油尖旺防火委員會 委員<br />\n人力資源規劃委員會 委員"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉國謙親人 侄兒"},{"pid":"79d13693df0fa9889cc78731abea3d7b536a1f72","tid":1945854,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"做呢啲濕鳩委員幾錢個月<br />\n定係有油水抽"},{"pid":"014a451c7c39473457d60efd1e0d6ee1376a15f1","tid":1945854,"uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/90441739_199935634761061_3539314469383438336_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=aDbG0sjVRwcAX80ttZe&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=5d3a69edb0d5609830f184f4f05066fd&amp;oe=5EA35F45\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x